{"tid":819972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Kickstarter 爛尾 Yashica Y35 相機又爛埋個Nano Combo淘寶熨斗","createTime":"2018-09-15T07:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T16:12:33.000Z","uid":209408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3bfa811cfc054cefed9322c88786e2cd91ab7a","tid":819972,"uid":209408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"早排都有好多網友講緊 Kickstarter 爛尾 Yashica Y35 <br />\n而家仲要搞爛埋個Nano Combo淘寶熨斗<br />\n<br />\n事源係有一間香港公司（唔知定係大陸公司），扮曬係日本公司，拎左個Yashica代理番黎，係Kickstarter 出個project 要整部數碼扮lomo 相機，之後有成千上萬的網友因為以為日本總公司，所以就比曬錢佢地整啦<br />\n<br />\n本來係2018年3月出貨的，而家2018年仲有3個月就完啦，都仲未有貨，好多backer 都大為緊張！好明顯就係想做Kickstarter 咖啡機2.0 <br />\n<br />\nFacebook 有曬苦主group （Yashica Y35 camera Fan club(Kickstarter &amp; Indiegogo)）<br />\nYashica facebook 都比人人唱衰佢嫁啦 （<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yashicaofficial/）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyashicaofficial%2F%EF%BC%89&d=%2FJ%2FZ3zBmxpWOjrIK420Ekk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=665cfd1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yashicaofficial/）</a><br />\n<br />\n仲要公司主管，老細都要比人起曬底<br />\n<br />\n之後到而家同公司一個project ，都比人搞爛埋，拎d 淘寶扮係全球第一，真係面就自已掉曬！<br />\n而家爛埋個Nano Combo淘寶熨斗～佢地間公司錢又搵少左啦一定！<br />\n（<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lifeisbeautiful/nano-combo-worlds-1st-nano-steam-iron-combo-by-jnc/comments）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Flifeisbeautiful%2Fnano-combo-worlds-1st-nano-steam-iron-combo-by-jnc%2Fcomments%EF%BC%89&d=%2FJ%2FZ3zBmxpWOjrIK420Ekk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=a01a73ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/lifeisbeautiful/nano-combo-worlds-1st-nano-steam-iron-combo-by-jnc/comments）</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYashica 重返相機戰線<br />\n傳送門 ＞<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/431238/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/431238/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都訂左yashica y35<br />\n傳送門 ＞<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/778643/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/778643/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n成地花生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9c22e031b99ca63573148d1f9db884f6548a10","tid":819972,"uid":64073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"就算佢誠實咁出到貨 件野本身都係一舊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f03d0a7995ac94c9fe70414f6d70990ef51bc9a","tid":819972,"uid":81045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:05:15.000Z","msg":"佢個新project 俾kickstarter停咗<br />\nFunding Suspended <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee7dcacaab38cd1b17a80be294d9f3be7444806","tid":819972,"uid":209408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:12:58.000Z","msg":"真件事，係唔係新手法用黎騙人，拎走曬d 錢！之後唔出貨<br />\n<br />\nor 出件垃圾出黎，根本都無人管到<br />\n咁好似！"},{"pid":"ad024d6e600e04be66ba1323f073c2a23ff1223f","tid":819972,"uid":209408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9c22e031b99ca63573148d1f9db884f6548a10","tid":819972,"uid":64073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"就算佢誠實咁出到貨 件野本身都係一舊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:14:17.000Z","msg":"好多人都係買佢個brand 姐，點知咩都係假，日本係假，model 係假，相機唔洗講啦"},{"pid":"92c068261fa9ec27830aeb0fac79be035ad02689","tid":819972,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br 